englishDescription: RiseSun Real Estate Development Co., Ltd is a China-based company, principally engaged in real estate development and distribution. The Company is mainly engaged in the development of ordinary commercial housings, such as residential properties, complementary shops, as well as garages, among others. In addition, the Company is also engaged in the provision of property management services and operation of hotels. The Company operates its businesses in domestic markets, including Hebei Province, Jiangsu Province, Shandong Province, Anhui Province and Hunan Province, among others.
